title: File:Harris Faulkner in Half Moone Cruise Terminal.jpg
author: U.S. Navy photo by Mass Communication Specialist Seaman Maxwell Anderson/Released
description: 180704-N-AG490-0529 NORFOLK (July 4, 2018) Harris Faulkner, a news anchor for Fox News, speaks with an audience during a symposium in the Half Moone Cruise Terminal during the 36th Annual Great American Picnic. The Great American Picnic is a free annual event that takes place on Independence Day and is open to both civilians and military members. (U.S. Navy photo by Mass Communication Specialist Seaman Maxwell Anderson/Released)
